          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Psi-Like Abilities:</strong></span> 3/day-<span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch56.html#PsionicPowersA-C41">brain lock</a></em></span> (affects animals, fey, <a href="ch66s06.html#MonstersG67">giants</a>, humanoids, magical beasts, and monstrous humanoids, DC 15*), <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch57.html#PsionicPowersD-F24">dimension slide</a></em></span>, <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch57.html#PsionicPowersD-F61">ego whip</a></em></span> (1d4, DC 15*)<span class="emphasis"><em/></span>,  <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch58.html#PsionicPowersG-P39">mental barrier</a></em></span>,  <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch58.html#PsionicPowersG-P61">mind thrust</a></em></span> (ML 4th, 4d10<span class="emphasis"><em/></span>, <span class="emphasis"><em/></span> DC 15*), <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch59.html#PsionicPowersQ-W27">skate</a></em></span>; 1/day-<span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch56.html#PsionicPowersA-C34">body adjustment</a></em></span> (heal 1d12*), <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch56.html#PsionicPowersA-C49">catapsi</a></em></span> (DC 18). Manifester level 6th. The save DCs are Charisma-based.</p>
